        def youtube_playlist_description_data
          {:playlist=>{:description=>"Enter the world of the Black Constellation in preparation for KEXP’s upcoming podcast, Fresh off the Spaceship. The podcast will chart the influential artist collective’s path from a seed in our backyard in Seattle, Washington to an entity with cosmic reach. Black Constellation has encompassed such innovative and varied musical acts as Shabazz Palaces (helmed by Ishmael Butler of Grammy-award winning trio Digable Planets), Stas THEE Boss (formerly of THEESatisfaction), Erik Blood, OCnotes, Porter Ray, JusMoni, and Nicholas Galanin (Ya Tseen). It also includes visual and literary artists Maikoiyo Alley-Barnes and Nep Sidhu.\n\nHosted by KEXP’s Larry Mizell Jr. and Martin Douglas, each of the 10 episodes will take listeners on a musical journey connecting the stars of the Black Constellation and drawing meaning from their art, emphasizing the revolutionary power of communion along the way.\n\nFind out more: https://www.kexp.org/fresh-off-the-spaceship/\n\nSubscribe now wherever you get your podcasts:\n\nApple Podcasts \nhttps://apple.co/3hvidDZ\n\nStitcher \nhttps://bit.ly/3MgUGVl\n\nSpotify \nhttps://spoti.fi/3C9xPWU\n\nGoogle Podcasts \nhttps://bit.ly/3syXwgr\n\nAmazon Music \nhttps://amzn.to/3tojeD9\n\nPocket Casts \nhttps://bit.ly/3tr34c3\n\n\nPodcast cover art by Todd Westendorp.\n\nhttps://www.kexp.org/"}}          
